Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.21,0:00:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.23,0:00:03.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}不必消去这份记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:05.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人生不是还很漫长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}那些没有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:12.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:28.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}明明一直在追赶着梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:35.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}跌跌撞撞地走在弯曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:38.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不奢望回到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:41.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是在苦寻那片丢失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:43.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像你明白一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:48.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}除去那像牺牲之后的悲伤表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}罪孽之后并不是泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而是一直以来背负的苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}迷失在没有出口的情感迷宫中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:55.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在等待着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像在白色笔记本上刻画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:58.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很想诚实地说出心声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:00.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在逃避什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:02.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}…原来是叫做现实的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:05.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了实现愿望而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不禁想要大喊  你能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:13.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}平安无事却让人没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}…无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.24,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感谢同伴们带来的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}所以要更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:27.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}这种痛苦也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:33.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:38.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:44.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}约定和契约  被初夏的微风所怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:48.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:57.54,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在强颜欢笑的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:02.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}隐藏着逐渐扩大的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:12.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以  只装做没有发现  选择了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:21.69,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}在桌边继续等待那没有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:30.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在空白的夜里  无法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:34.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}其实我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:40.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:45.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}总有一天会想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:51.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}抱着没有实现的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:55.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人一起出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 快到达普利斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做梦了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是那家伙的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅若是不在家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了 长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会…会变矮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我是阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成铠甲之后 第一次被人摸头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米 艾尔利克那小不点来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 今天感觉还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体不好 正在睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不清楚身体有没有好转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这笨蛋弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你做了军队的走狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 你长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅也还是老样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锻炼不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不是身体不适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 还不是因为你们来了 所以这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬撑可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在担心我吗 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于贤者之石 我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 在中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是遇到过一个对石头非常熟知的炼金术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是以前离家出走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙的错 妈妈死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这么一大早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔要尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在帮我照顾阿尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 关于石头 父亲说过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说长年的愿望马上就要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在火车里吃了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 阿尔 我们在拉修巴雷帮忙接生了婴儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:06:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 我们帮忙接生了婴儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那个怎么算是帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家人合力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲也是拚命努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在众人的祝福下 孩子出生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也是这样获得了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对自己的生命感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那个时候开始就没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再搬点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堤坝要决口了 快逃到高处去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样应该能撑一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是路过的主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收我们做弟子吧 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微有点耳背 没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们订正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收我们做弟子吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的原则是不收弟子的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我还在旅行的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 收我们做弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双亲的许可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…这两个孩子没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得这么柔弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠你们自己活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是预备修行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功的话就进入正式修行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在预备修行中禁止使用炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一即是全 全即是一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个月内找到这个问题的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到答案的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把你们送回利塞布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在床上睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算哪门子炼金术的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个小鬼不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比经验更好的知识了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让他们记住炼金术的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个方法是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样还学不到任何东西的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 他们只有那么点才能而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让他们放弃做我的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是否会有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我修行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是被扔在冬季的布里克斯山里一个月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把你和一般人相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个岛上食物也很丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要怎么吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俐落地砍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俐落地？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 哥哥来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是负责捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是把麻烦的事情推给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃肉 去吃鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么抓鱼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼竿 鱼线和鱼钩都没有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有食物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你干什么呀 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好酸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃着蚂蚁活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃着生命活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到明天就是一个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“一即是全 全即是一”的答案找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只有朦胧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然无法确信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿得意识不清的时候 我吃过蚂蚁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常酸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后考虑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没吃 饿死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被狐狸和蚂蚁吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成土地 成为草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后草被兔子吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是食物炼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个岛在很久以前说不定是沉在海底的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过几万年 说不定会变成山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说世上万物都有联系？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都在眼睛看不到的大潮流中存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是叫宇宙还是世界 虽然还不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于那个大东西来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿尔就像蚂蚁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潮流中渺小的一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是“全”中的“一”而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那渺小的“一”聚集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“全”才能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到约定的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我听听“一即是全 全即是一”的答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“全”是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“一”是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入正式修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼成阵的基本是圆的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圆显示着力量的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里描绘构筑式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以发动力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是力量的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（紧张）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用身体来感受是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 在午饭准备好之前好好复习
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圆显示着力量的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里描绘构筑式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以发动力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 师傅只是两只手掌一合就能炼成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要描绘构筑式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自身就像是构筑式一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样才能做到？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果触及到真理的话 说不定就能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅也看到了真理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不用构筑式就能进行炼成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上阿尔冯斯只是个空壳铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是单手单脚机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点事情一交手就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看过那个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:18:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看过了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师徒都这样 真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅也看过了那个 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们夫妇 怎么也怀不上孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易我怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却因为我生病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的孩子没能活着降临人世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯下了禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 身体里很多东西都被取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该早点告诉你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是自己干的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦这种心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果取回身体 要吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而变得很期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这两个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界遵从着无法想像的巨大法则而流动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解这个流动 分析之后 再进行构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也是生存本身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分解以及再构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.84,0:21:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和食物炼一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了兔子 它的肉就被分解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再构筑成自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把吃的草再构筑成自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是生命本身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陶醉于自己欲望之中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是敌是友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他们面前出现的那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是只为了战斗而诞生的异形
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.89,0:24:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十三话 达普利斯的野兽们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者现身

